Class Log

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.checkout_simulator.simulation.Log

  • public class Log
extends java.lang.Object
    A class used to keep track of the statistics for how long it takes carts to check out and how long they wait in line prior to checking out.
